entries.text: Your web support advisor today is Jen, from the XYZ Live Chat team
Welcome to XYZ's help and support web team
Secure forms are enabled during this chat session
Hi User 28, my #ALNUM Jen. How may I help you today
I would like to add breakdown cover to the Yaris on this policy. I cannot add on line as I have just added a new vehicle to the policy that starts on #NUM

As you have made a change on the policy for a future date we cannot make any other changes until that date either. This is a system condition as all changes have to be done in date order. You can then add the breakdown cover to the policy online just as we can but cover cannot start until #ALNUM
Thank you. So i should have done it the other way round
The changes need to be made in date order unfortunately so if changes are made for dates in the future it essentially freezes the policy from any other changes until that date.
ke a note to add it on #ALNUM
You can make that addition online but you'd need to state that the cover would be from #NUM when that other changes is effective from.
